body:
@KRTirtho, I have a question about this feature. How should it work?
I have the current version 3.6.0 on Windows, Mac and Android and had thought that I would be able to stream my music to my HiFi Berry or my Sonos sound system from there or control my Mac or Windows PC from my Android. Or have I misunderstood?

"Only" locally connected Bluetooth could be selected among the devices when I connect it to my JBL speaker.
